Package fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.processors

Contains all processors, exporters/importers and validators for EmotionML.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
EmotionMLExporter A EmotionMLExporter is an EmotionMLProcessor that exports EmotionML objects in an OutputStream by first building DOM elements corresponding to them then validating them.
EmotionMLImporter A EmotionMLImporter imports EmotionML elements from the InputStream by first reading the stream as a DOM Element, then by validating the DOM Element with respect to the EmotionML standard and eventually by building EmotionML objects.
EmotionMLProcessor An EmotionMLProcessor is a basic class that holds a reference to an EmotionMLValidator.
EmotionMLValidator A EmotionMLValidator is an object which validates the EmotionML elements with regards to the specification (see EmotionML specification).
ValidationResult ValidationResult gathers the results of a validation.
VocabularyResolver A VocabularyResolvert helps the retrieval and parsing of documents during a serialization or deserialization operation.
